# EU Governance Lab — Mapping Controls to NIS2/GDPR

**Analyst:** Melissa Wozney  

---

## 1. Executive summary

This lab explored how cloud security controls map to EU regulatory requirements, focusing on NIS2 and GDPR‑related expectations for logging, access control, and incident response.

---

## 2. Objectives

- Identify relevant NIS2/GDPR themes (availability, integrity, confidentiality).
- Map technical controls (IAM, logging, IR) to governance requirements.
- Document a simple control mapping table.

---

## 3. Example control mapping

| Control area      | Cloud control example              | Regulatory theme        |
|-------------------|------------------------------------|-------------------------|
| Access control    | IAM roles & least privilege        | Confidentiality         |
| Logging & audit   | CloudTrail / audit logs            | Accountability, IR      |
| Incident response | IR runbooks & playbooks            | Resilience, reporting   |

